Package src

Class WGraph_DS

java.lang.Object
src.WGraph_DS
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, weighted_graph
public class WGraph_DS
extends java.lang.Object
implements weighted_graph, java.io.Serializable
This class represents an weighted graph. It should support a large number of nodes (over 10^6, with average degree of 10). The implementation should be based on an efficient compact representation
Author:
Alex Baranov

    • equals

      public boolean equals​(java.lang.Object obj)
      Equals function, overrides the object equals method and implements a new equals method. This new equals method runs on both graphs and checks if they both got the same values. It checks the key, weight values, also checks if all the connections are the same,also checks node, mc and edge sizes.
      Overrides:
      equals in class java.lang.Object
      Parameters:
      obj - The graph you wish to compare it to,
      Returns:
      boolean true if both graphs are the same, false if even 1 param is different.
